AUDIO: 'What\'s up Sumo lings? It\'s Chloe from AppSumo, the best place to get insane deals on business software. Today we\'re checking out Puzzle, a visual workspace that helps you map processes, link tools and roles, and track time and cost. Running a business often means your'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'processes live in a dozen different places. Spreadsheets, Slack threads, random docs, and no one sees the full picture. That leads to confusion, wasted spend, and tools that don\'t actually work together. Puzzle fixes all of that with a visual workspace that maps every'

[00:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'step, links your tools and team, and even tracks time and cost so you can finally run your operations with clarity. To get rolling, hop into the workflow canvas. It\'s like your master blueprint. Click on any step and boom, you\'ll see the role, the tool, notes,'

[00:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'even Loom or Scribe videos all in one spot. Add your own notes or embeds, and suddenly you\'ve got a visual playbook anyone can follow. Switch over to the team canvas to see who\'s tackling what, or jump into the tool canvas to spot'

[00:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'exactly how many steps are tied to each app in your stack. Puzzle gives you a bird\'s-eye view of your entire operations database, so you can finally see how every step connects to a tool, a teammate, and even the cost behind it.'

[01:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'When you click on a step, Puzzle doesn\'t just give you a label. It opens up the whole story in the sidebar. You\'ll see the role, the tools, notes, and even Loom or Scribe videos, so every process comes with built-in context. It\'s like turning your workflows into a visual'

[01:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'playbook your team can actually follow instead of guessing what\'s next. The integration sync sidebar pulls live items straight from HubSpot, Make, and Zapier, flagging anything you haven\'t mapped yet and letting you drop it onto the canvas with one click. And with the'

[01:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'tool canvas, you get superhero level vision into your whole tech stack, showing exactly where every app is used and what it\'s costing you. With Puzzle\'s costing layer, you don\'t have to guess where your time and money are going. It\'s all laid out step by step. You\'ll'

[01:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'see exactly how much labor, tool spend, and effort each part of a process eats up. Think of it like an instant ROI dashboard, pointing you straight to the spots where trimming costs or making tweaks will have the biggest payoff. Think of it like x-ray vision for your'

[01:53] [scene:talk]
