AUDIO: 'tech stack. You\'ll see every app, exactly where it\'s being used, and how much it\'s costing you. It\'s the fastest way to spot overlap, cut out the SAS bloat, and make sure you\'re only paying for tools that actually pull their weight. Puzzle brings clarity to the'

